trans-unit.source: Contains the classes used to instrument your application.
trans-unit.target: Contiene le classi usate per instrumentare l'applicazione.

trans-unit.source: The instrumentation, when enabled, logs the event data to the Event Tracing for Windows (ETW) tracing subsystem.
trans-unit.target: La strumentazione, quando abilitata, registra i dati degli eventi nel sottosistema di traccia Event Tracing for Windows (ETW).

trans-unit.source: For a complete description of ETW, see <see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows-hardware/drivers/devtest/event-tracing-for-windows--etw-">Event Tracing for Windows</see>.
trans-unit.target: Per una descrizione completa di ETW, vedere <see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows-hardware/drivers/devtest/event-tracing-for-windows--etw-">Event Tracing for Windows</see>.
